{{flavour|Launches a small hail of sharp thorns.}}

'''Volley of Thorns''' is a monster-only spell which blasts you with a spray of deadly spines, dealing heavy ranged physical damage.

{{monsters with spell}}

Also, [[Fedhas]] can sometimes punish disloyal followers with a Volley of Thorns.

==History==
*Volley of Thorns was added in [[0.14]].

